						               													<description>In Mini Macaroon Madness, your job is to get trays of macaroons out to customers quickly. Mix up flavors and combinations in the right amount to earn favor and become the best macaroon baker.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Components&amp;#10;12 Macaroon Tokens&amp;#10;36 Macaroon Tray Cards&amp;#10;8 Dice&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Set Up &amp;amp; Quick Play&amp;#10;Shuffle macaroon tokens and macaron tray cards.&amp;#10;Lay out a grid with 4 macarons on both the left and right. Roll the dice and make 4 columns on the top and bottom.  Leave space for macaron tray cards to be laid out in a 4x4 grid. Each player receives 4 macaron tray cards.&amp;#10;On your turn, play as many macaron trays into the grid as possible. They need to match one of the two dice options and 1 of the 2 macaron options. Special action cards allow you to add to your turn. Use all 4 cards and receive 4 more. Continue to play until you are unable to play and then restock to 4 cards and end your turn.&amp;#10;When players complete a vertical column, they receive an extra macaron card and roll a die in the column. They may continue their turn.&amp;#10;When players complete a horizontal row, they score 1 point. They change up one of the two macarons and continue their turn.  They may score additional points during their turn in that same row if they can place at least one macaron tray.  When they are unable to play the row of trays is placed in the discard pile.  &amp;#10;Play continues until a player scores 6 points.  Keep track of your score on paper.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
